aims:
教養英会話 is a practice‑based course aimed at continuing to develop communicative and conversational skills in English. The course objectives are as follows:
‑ to provide students with an environment in which they can communicate in English;
‑ to develop English communication skills with a focus on speaking and listening;
‑ to develop an operational understanding of grammar —particularly spoken grammar— and typical patterns and cogs in the target language;
‑ to provide cultural input related to the target language and provide opportunities to converse on a variety of topics;
‑ to build awareness of the socially appropriate use of language according to context;
‑ to foster fluency and improve listening skills;
‑ to foster intercultural understanding.

